{"tid":711143,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"＊[趕住投胎]牙藍的即日來回live之旅","createTime":"2018-06-21T10:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T11:10:32.000Z","uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b6a468033150fe56414c3c8943da665a4e71a6d9","tid":711143,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:07:41.000Z","msg":"好耐無開過post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排好悶又屎忽痕決定開下post分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖劣用ipx影 都無乜圖無乜字 純粹真係分享下唔係咩包膠乜乜柒柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n識我既知就算 相認就唔洗鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次去既live就係6月1號遠藤ゆりか既final live<br />\n雖然唔算得上係推佢, 不過都叫睇左成年Roselia...<br />\n點都有d感情既.. 最後一場又咁岩通販自己撳到張飛就決定左去了<br />\n今次坐jetstar既去程 凌晨2點GK20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一上機就比哂入境紙唔似UO/香草之類飛到一半先派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此po含有0.01%動漫成分</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180026_49694ce0f3f6abc4782b56395e09604a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180026_49694ce0f3f6abc4782b56395e09604a.jpg&h=72e059ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前係7仔買既朱古力... 好撚好食... 未起飛已經食哂成盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果訓醒起哂痰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180026_a6dfd2cbb4ff8fbb92eb1fccb17cb9ee.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180026_a6dfd2cbb4ff8fbb92eb1fccb17cb9ee.jpg&h=72533112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第朝7點幾到成田<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n程機都算訓到下, 不過都仲係好眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180026_d1ca0e5a1412b365684f261e9f927ce1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180026_d1ca0e5a1412b365684f261e9f927ce1.jpg&h=4778f553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180026_71745c9b567061cb8d428af06ad35178.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180026_71745c9b567061cb8d428af06ad35178.jpg&h=45bf76b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nT3見到既TIGER底褲仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180026_c421c99f8966cf9220fb14522b5ac376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180026_c421c99f8966cf9220fb14522b5ac376.jpg&h=2a55e5dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去埋ATM撳錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次撳一萬算 計埋上次用剩既<br />\n今日洗萬2YEN應該夠哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180026_f27924c146f500f377e881d99c8d7f1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180026_f27924c146f500f377e881d99c8d7f1e.jpg&h=d06d90be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d15a621b2857e9dcd46deb93e7a329f58251588","tid":711143,"uid":34858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> push"},{"pid":"8b09f34a3836492d888591c54a094983dedd72ba","tid":711143,"uid":21456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:18:17.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"91c0ca7f1d54ad048760d550a716156983f20864","tid":711143,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"話就話係飛機訓左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但家下先7點 都仲係好撚眼訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗住一心去休息室訓陣, 訓到咁上下先出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180809_01cc05d30125017fd7b1bb7965d6cd90.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180809_01cc05d30125017fd7b1bb7965d6cd90.jpg&h=e0d03bda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母咩.... 跟住係T2到坐下坐咁下 hea到10點零鐘就出老秋搵fd算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180809_fc478b53da8cbf0fe0d3739d5b076642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180809_fc478b53da8cbf0fe0d3739d5b076642.jpg&h=5788aeee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nd人成日呃鳩人第一次去既, 咩成田坐skyliner/nex個d舒服又快<br />\n其實坐巴士好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1000yen程直出東京站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又平又快, 計過下其實一粒鐘鬆d到已經到東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自從識坐之後好耐無坐過電車來回成田<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180809_070ba492f21e6cfdb71077580ad9d69f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180809_070ba492f21e6cfdb71077580ad9d69f.jpg&h=fad35a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180809_ffcc68b628acb6c03608aafb383583b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180809_ffcc68b628acb6c03608aafb383583b7.jpg&h=500420fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n粒零鐘之後 已經到左老秋<br />\n咁岩車站對出間sega做緊P5主題影返幅相打卡先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180810_1fd80b1b69c6287fb3c1b413614e91c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180810_1fd80b1b69c6287fb3c1b413614e91c3.jpg&h=e08188b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫朋友買碟送既特典...屌你老母咁撚高質既....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180810_3fe18897612e53c4399d1497ff487a4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180810_3fe18897612e53c4399d1497ff487a4e.jpg&h=26d16838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180810_0e799876fc44f08808b53e8dcdae4d04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180810_0e799876fc44f08808b53e8dcdae4d04.jpg&h=aaadf512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後行左幾粒鐘老秋, 一心諗住想搵下HOTTOY隻STARLORD, 睇下日本會唔會平D<br />\n點知搵極都無, 終於見到有個盒幾似果時一拎上手...<br />\n屌你老母乜撚野事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180810_760bdb8b8492844856b4bdb15d4947bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180810_760bdb8b8492844856b4bdb15d4947bd.jpg&h=311d60ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到咁上下就去左同朋友食LUNCH之後準備去會場買下物販+搵朋友了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n千零YEN幾好食 算係咁<br />\n飯可湯可以任加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/180811_1e2fc237a99946450bb25f90c68e0825.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F180811_1e2fc237a99946450bb25f90c68e0825.jpg&h=864abea9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8c20e7a0a91f89731ad34f83daf2ad9b3e20af4","tid":711143,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"去到會場出面 都真係幾多人<br />\n事前睇Twitter見到好多架仔晨早徹夜去排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我點零兩點鐘先去到 諗住去到執下有乜賣唔出既貨尾當留念算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/182057_a3a433c963aa1c5e67b83636c1a0c993.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F182057_a3a433c963aa1c5e67b83636c1a0c993.jpg&h=7d30ed00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n物販最後尾張野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求撚奇搵張紙皮潦幾隻字當係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紙皮都得 咁condom都得啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/182057_bac707e97c24e3d58db5cd1140c9de8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F182057_bac707e97c24e3d58db5cd1140c9de8e.jpg&h=4391fb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好意外地 d貨量都備得好足下 識唔少人幾套全set咁買<br />\n但到我果時竟然都仲好多仲有貨<br />\n當日物販買夠3千5yen可以抽一下 有直筆poster之類既景品抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買夠3千5yen抽一下算...咁當然都好理所當然咁係唔中任何野既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/182057_122b250a73b330a5c0814f22f36cf549.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F182057_122b250a73b330a5c0814f22f36cf549.jpg&h=78c2db02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我今日個位幾乎係最後既 個場好似最盡開得1298人<br />\n我就1294<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 索性開場先入算 反正咁早入去又係罰企<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/182058_a82ddabe618e431bac1170b453fbfb58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F182058_a82ddabe618e431bac1170b453fbfb58.jpg&h=2772c0eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n班人已經列緊隊入場<br />\n其實唔止圖入面咁少 條隊係樓梯上面都繼續有好多人排緊<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/182058_358d1258a9f586756c7a42a26844b754.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F182058_358d1258a9f586756c7a42a26844b754.jpg&h=1f24aee4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n至於呢到就係買唔到飛睇唔到live 但都一心過黎想買下goods既隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係一樣好多人<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/182058_494d69da268313775f3837d9dbe1bccb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F182058_494d69da268313775f3837d9dbe1bccb.jpg&h=147d982e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到7點咁上下 d人終於入哂場<br />\n我都可以起身行了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/182058_7bc3c85af0b7fc476e116a0017d9aa42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F182058_7bc3c85af0b7fc476e116a0017d9aa42.jpg&h=fed83127&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會場內既圖都無乜<br />\n完場都趕時間入機場所以無乜點影相<br />\n場live比想像中長 畢竟都係最後一次...<br />\n包膠叫春個d都無乜<br />\n話唔捨得就肯定既<br />\n不過引退呢條路係遠藤自己揀 作為fans都剩係得支持佢呢個選擇吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝佢未來一片光明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd87f3cb694528ad272f88867a1ead3fd0277b80","tid":711143,"uid":58038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"生死時速咁<br />\n一完場就即刻走<br />\n好彩我個number後企得後<br />\n近住出口 一完場就即刻推門走得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/183112_e7b30a634640454fd0f8de02ff0979f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F183112_e7b30a634640454fd0f8de02ff0979f4.jpg&h=10d7be63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到羽田之後拿拿聲去沖個涼跟手就online checkin左入禁區食野等上機了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/183113_de554444765c0bfe22a0c40784c1e725.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F183113_de554444765c0bfe22a0c40784c1e725.jpg&h=a6d21cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個沾麵算ok啦不過不失<br />\n但肯定係貴過出面架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/183113_a5bdde0b7571c1f0a69e519bcaf557d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F183113_a5bdde0b7571c1f0a69e519bcaf557d7.jpg&h=7e3ce542&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔記得左講.. 回程唔係jetstar<br />\n係坐UO 623 羽田凌晨一點鐘機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有坐過呢班既都知 個gate幾乎係機場既盡頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/183113_acc5b4893a34f98b7eac4e4efe8ed4f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F183113_acc5b4893a34f98b7eac4e4efe8ed4f8.jpg&h=9fdf0126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/183113_3e18516f211a55a511a7977484a85d4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F183113_3e18516f211a55a511a7977484a85d4a.jpg&h=7fd09ffd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上機走得<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/183113_c2b5bc43b1861ec5ac7bfe143054eb1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F183113_c2b5bc43b1861ec5ac7bfe143054eb1e.jpg&h=5f7a0a27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n返到香港入境先4點半鬆d 仲未有車返屋企住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/183114_5e3788ed2146f6b9e7119245ba507a36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F183114_5e3788ed2146f6b9e7119245ba507a36.jpg&h=1cdb9072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終於等到巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩好破曉<br />\n對應返遠藤既最後一個主題Daybreak吧...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/183114_d5018c1a87a7eca3f335216ee2edeb28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F183114_d5018c1a87a7eca3f335216ee2edeb28.jpg&h=abc9550d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34f54f184fc00d3803352b8e7e46bcf457e22d8","tid":711143,"uid":150609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T10:41:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4138c8ec7c10af130fdbbea5bb82fd2ec072ac66","tid":711143,"uid":679,"like":0,"disl